RACE.FOOTNOTES: PURE CONNECTION was settled while inside in the early going, saved ground on the turn then slipped through the inside in upper stretch to take command and was in a strong drive and held sway in the end. MIDNIGHT LADY stumbled badly at the start and was unhurried, started a run on the turn and swung out to be six wide in upper stretch and closed fast on the outside to finished fastest of all. MISS YOU NO MORE chased the early pace while three wide into the turn, rallied on the turn and put a head in front in upper stretch but weakened in late stretch. MONTANA'S ANGEL chased the early pace while inside, made a bid and moved out to be four wide in upper stretch, was in a hard drive but came up empty in late stretch. MO WILLA dueled for the lead while inside, was in a long drive but faltered in late stretch. LADY YELLOWSTONE was allowed to settled then rallied three wide on the turn and failed to menace. DE DE'S BIRD was unhurried early then raced five wide on the turn and was no threat. FULL MOON BEACH dueled for the lead while two wide into the turn, was used up then gave way. HOLIDAY PRESENCE was unhurried early then failed to menace. PURR TIGER chased the early pace while two wide into the turn, was used up and stopped in the stretch.
